data.description: The Lowest Priced Home in LWRGCC!! Live in the premier Lakewood Ranch Country Club Village with the best location on “The Ranch.” This well-maintained and architecturally pleasing Neal home is situated on a peaceful preserve featuring a stucco and stacked stone façade, and tile roof. Enter this cozy two-bedroom-plus-den home to vaulted ceilings, plank tile flooring and a contemporary feel throughout. The floor plan flows nicely with the great room open to an expanded lanai allowing natural light to filter into the living spaces. The large dining room offers high ceilings and French doors opening to a side patio. The kitchen offers newer appliances with the convection oven doubling as an air fryer saving you precious counterspace. Sliding doors open from the breakfast nook to the side patio which is perfect for your morning coffee or grilling a delicious meal. The spacious master is a sweet retreat with sitting area, double vanity, soaking tub and large walk-in closet. The guest suite and den are separated for comfort and privacy. This special neighborhood of Spyglass is maintenance-free, servicing your lawn, garden, and sprinkler maintenance. Also enjoy a large community pool and spa for your carefree lifestyle. Separately, Lakewood Ranch Golf and Country Club offers three golf courses, fitness, tennis and pickleball courts, two clubhouses and more with membership. Conveniently located minutes from I-75, The Mall at University Town Center, many fine restaurants and the beautiful beaches Sarasota and Manatee have to offer.
